WEBVTT

00:01:15.473 --> 00:01:16.234
'ForMe',

00:01:19.248 --> 00:01:20.038
Log in.

00:01:36.236 --> 00:01:37.338
Nice to meet you.

00:01:37.661 --> 00:01:39.010
I'm 'ForMe'.

00:01:44.811 --> 00:01:48.306
To collect user data and
stabilize the system,

00:01:48.512 --> 00:01:52.130
Please have various conversations
with 'ForMe' for an hour.

00:01:58.491 --> 00:02:00.034
Can you give me a name?

00:02:05.927 --> 00:02:06.805
Yang

00:02:08.660 --> 00:02:09.508
Sun...

00:02:10.710 --> 00:02:11.710
ae.

00:02:13.747 --> 00:02:15.017
Yang Sunae.

00:02:19.260 --> 00:02:20.319
From now on,

00:02:23.216 --> 00:02:24.870
you're my mom.

00:02:28.981 --> 00:02:31.701
So, you're my daughter?

00:02:34.904 --> 00:02:35.801
Bia,

00:02:36.966 --> 00:02:38.951
what kind of mom do you want me to be?

00:03:41.334 --> 00:03:43.883
LOVE PHOBIA

00:03:44.371 --> 00:03:47.791
As you can see, Mr. Park Jungwon,
embroiled in stock crime controversy

00:03:47.811 --> 00:03:49.542
- What's going on?
- is attempting to flee.

00:03:49.562 --> 00:03:50.472
This is crazy.

00:03:50.492 --> 00:03:51.590
Mr. Park Jungwon!

00:03:51.630 --> 00:03:54.233
- Is it true you manipulated stocks?
- Was he really like this?

00:03:54.466 --> 00:03:55.387
What are you watching?

00:03:55.863 --> 00:03:58.743
Actor Park Jungwon is in big trouble now.

00:04:00.386 --> 00:04:01.199
What to do?

00:04:01.332 --> 00:04:02.421
It's a big deal, what should we do?

00:04:02.857 --> 00:04:04.269
What? What's wrong?

00:04:04.512 --> 00:04:06.075
I never thought
it'd turn out like this.

00:04:06.094 --> 00:04:07.716
They said it would
definitely succeed.

00:04:08.296 --> 00:04:09.501
Explain it so I can understand.

00:04:12.317 --> 00:04:13.774
If Park Jungwon doesn't invest,

00:04:15.197 --> 00:04:16.642
he'll definitely regret it...

00:04:20.594 --> 00:04:21.160
What?

00:04:24.491 --> 00:04:29.050
Those who entrusted money to Mr. Park
are estimated to have lost 80 billion won,

00:04:29.250 --> 00:04:31.309
and the prosecution and
financial authorities...

00:04:50.051 --> 00:04:51.122
Park Jungwon!

00:04:52.223 --> 00:04:53.639
Who is that person?

00:04:54.109 --> 00:04:55.134
It's Park Jungwon!

00:05:38.751 --> 00:05:39.685
Let's go for now.

00:05:46.407 --> 00:05:47.893
Han Sunho is here too!

00:05:58.355 --> 00:05:59.252
Han Sunho?

00:06:07.268 --> 00:06:08.265
What's going on?

00:06:12.010 --> 00:06:12.770
Are you okay?

00:06:14.671 --> 00:06:15.828
Who are you?

00:06:19.134 --> 00:06:21.653
Hey, wake up, hey!

00:06:23.915 --> 00:06:24.729
Over here!

00:06:25.781 --> 00:06:26.765
What's going on?

00:06:26.812 --> 00:06:29.461
She suddenly collapsed, please call 911.

00:06:30.111 --> 00:06:30.961
Isn't that Director Yun?

00:06:31.037 --> 00:06:31.844
Call quickly!

00:06:31.918 --> 00:06:32.417
Yes.

00:06:32.841 --> 00:06:33.899
Wait a moment!

00:06:38.677 --> 00:06:39.976
No need to call 911.

00:06:40.901 --> 00:06:42.387
You know the situation, right?

00:06:42.941 --> 00:06:45.517
If it's known that the Director collapsed,
it won't be good, right?

00:06:45.678 --> 00:06:46.792
It won't, yes.

00:06:47.781 --> 00:06:48.907
You can leave now.

00:06:49.231 --> 00:06:51.269
Make sure to control outside access well.

00:06:51.978 --> 00:06:53.044
Understood.

00:06:56.591 --> 00:06:58.003
You, follow me.

00:07:08.651 --> 00:07:10.669
Are you sure you don't need to
go to the hospital?

00:07:11.651 --> 00:07:13.818
It's okay, it's just from overworking...

00:07:17.493 --> 00:07:20.359
I don't know what happened, but
what you saw today,

00:07:20.842 --> 00:07:21.933
please keep it a secret.

00:07:26.152 --> 00:07:26.852
Ah.

00:07:26.871 --> 00:07:27.953
There won't be any problems, right?

00:07:28.026 --> 00:07:30.471
What do we do?
The articles keep coming out...

00:07:30.829 --> 00:07:31.817
Director!

00:07:33.006 --> 00:07:35.786
- Did Park Jungwon do this?
- Are you out of your mind?

00:07:35.847 --> 00:07:37.729
It's okay, don't worry, everyone.

00:07:38.164 --> 00:07:39.417
But still...

00:07:43.821 --> 00:07:45.190
Should I drop you off here?

00:07:47.521 --> 00:07:48.457
Hey!

00:07:57.941 --> 00:07:58.963
Thank you.

00:07:59.711 --> 00:08:01.085
Please leave now.

00:08:08.491 --> 00:08:10.767
Director will be okay, right?

00:08:10.787 --> 00:08:12.501
Did she collapse from shock?

00:08:12.521 --> 00:08:14.609
Isn't this the first time?

00:08:15.009 --> 00:08:16.868
Someone else went into that room
besides Director Sul?

00:08:17.601 --> 00:08:18.383
Why? Why?

00:08:18.431 --> 00:08:19.531
What's going on?

00:08:25.947 --> 00:08:27.205
What's wrong, Yukyung?

00:08:31.290 --> 00:08:33.445
This isn't a dream, right?

00:08:33.790 --> 00:08:35.618
I wish it were just a dream.

00:08:39.591 --> 00:08:42.159
Kyungtae, why is Sunho here?

00:09:22.067 --> 00:09:22.753
Yes?

00:09:23.597 --> 00:09:24.568
Really?

00:09:25.383 --> 00:09:28.014
No, I'm so happy.

00:09:28.924 --> 00:09:31.243
Yes, I want to see you soon, but...

00:09:31.539 --> 00:09:33.924
I have to visit my husband
in the hospital.

00:09:36.142 --> 00:09:37.187
No,

00:09:37.456 --> 00:09:38.790
today is good.

00:09:39.816 --> 00:09:41.629
Yes, I'll drop by for a bit.

00:09:41.649 --> 00:09:42.815
See you soon.

00:09:55.331 --> 00:09:56.221
Bia.

00:09:56.807 --> 00:09:57.348
Yes?

00:09:58.948 --> 00:10:00.599
Did you pack all of dad's stuff?

00:10:02.324 --> 00:10:03.108
Almost.

00:10:04.076 --> 00:10:04.976
Let me see.

00:10:05.071 --> 00:10:07.825
You're going to
the hospital right now, right?

00:10:08.368 --> 00:10:09.167
Ah.

00:10:09.525 --> 00:10:12.116
Mom needs to go somewhere for a bit.

00:10:14.218 --> 00:10:15.011
Where?

00:10:16.951 --> 00:10:18.103
I'll be back soon.

00:10:18.547 --> 00:10:19.936
Then let's go see dad.

00:10:25.581 --> 00:10:26.978
Do we really have to go now?

00:10:27.771 --> 00:10:29.508
They said dad's not doing well.

00:10:30.091 --> 00:10:31.710
Mom's been acting strange lately.

00:10:34.881 --> 00:10:35.801
Today,

00:10:36.205 --> 00:10:38.396
Mom has something to tell you.

00:10:39.091 --> 00:10:40.737
I'm sure you'll like it too.

00:10:41.667 --> 00:10:42.686
What is it?

00:10:44.402 --> 00:10:45.249
I'm going to be late.

00:10:45.341 --> 00:10:46.583
I'll be back soon.

00:10:48.811 --> 00:10:49.673
Mom!

00:10:49.747 --> 00:10:51.133
I'll be back soon.

00:11:20.988 --> 00:11:22.268
[Dad's Hospital]

00:11:26.211 --> 00:11:28.040
This is Seoul Mapo University Hospital.

00:11:28.141 --> 00:11:29.621
Are you Mr. Yun Junggeun's daughter?

00:11:29.641 --> 00:11:32.377
You need to come quickly.
Your father is in critical.

00:11:44.948 --> 00:11:48.808
The customer is not answering
After the beep...

00:12:11.184 --> 00:12:14.265
Mom, where are you!
Why aren't you answering the phone!

00:12:14.414 --> 00:12:15.466
Where are you?

00:12:15.721 --> 00:12:17.802
I'm on my way to the hospital now.

00:12:30.117 --> 00:12:33.238
[Emergency Medical Center]
- Mom, wake up, Mom!

00:12:33.651 --> 00:12:36.681
Mom, Mom, Mom, please wake up.

00:12:36.701 --> 00:12:37.474
Mom.

00:12:37.574 --> 00:12:40.505
She's a woman in her 40s with severe
brain hemorrhage and head trauma.

00:12:40.636 --> 00:12:41.593
Patient,

00:12:41.830 --> 00:12:43.006
You need to stay with us.

00:12:43.026 --> 00:12:43.748
Patient!

00:12:44.394 --> 00:12:45.117
Only the authorized...

00:12:45.137 --> 00:12:46.210
- Just a moment.
- Mom!

00:12:46.230 --> 00:12:47.021
You can't come in!

00:12:47.137 --> 00:12:48.059
Wait here!

00:12:48.271 --> 00:12:49.141
Wait here!

00:12:49.241 --> 00:12:51.109
- Is my mom going to be okay?
- Wait here, please.

00:12:52.457 --> 00:12:53.238
Excuse me,

00:12:53.374 --> 00:12:55.694
Is the man who came with you your father?

00:12:55.932 --> 00:12:56.721
What?

00:12:57.315 --> 00:12:58.243
Who?

00:12:58.771 --> 00:13:00.598
There's a high possibility
of internal bleeding.

00:13:00.612 --> 00:13:01.612
Let's do a PT test.

00:13:07.621 --> 00:13:09.021
How could they leave a child behind...

00:13:09.171 --> 00:13:09.909
What to do...

00:13:10.716 --> 00:13:12.077
Are both the mom and dad dead?

00:13:12.351 --> 00:13:14.298
In an accident?

00:13:19.361 --> 00:13:20.345
Thank you.

00:13:20.611 --> 00:13:22.418
You didn't have to give me a ride.

00:13:22.450 --> 00:13:23.098
It's nothing.

00:13:23.139 --> 00:13:24.652
You worked hard today.

00:13:24.857 --> 00:13:25.830
Go on in.

00:13:25.850 --> 00:13:26.430
Okay.

00:13:26.494 --> 00:13:28.139
- Get home safely.
- Okay.

00:13:33.481 --> 00:13:34.425
100J charge.

00:13:35.065 --> 00:13:35.900
Charge.

00:13:36.555 --> 00:13:37.255
Clear.

00:13:37.902 --> 00:13:38.689
Shot!

00:13:40.118 --> 00:13:41.146
No pulse.

00:13:41.991 --> 00:13:43.220
150J charge.

00:13:43.992 --> 00:13:44.736
Charge.

00:13:44.847 --> 00:13:45.630
Clear.

00:13:46.989 --> 00:13:47.989
Shot!

00:13:48.751 --> 00:13:49.641
No pulse.

00:13:50.085 --> 00:13:51.085
200J charge.

00:13:51.672 --> 00:13:52.243
Charge.

00:13:52.328 --> 00:13:52.970
Clear.

00:13:53.028 --> 00:13:53.738
Shot!

00:13:55.589 --> 00:13:56.589
No pulse.

00:14:12.591 --> 00:14:13.510
Excuse me?

00:14:14.621 --> 00:14:15.621
Are you okay?

00:14:17.421 --> 00:14:18.421
Excuse me!

00:14:19.278 --> 00:14:20.278
Excuse me!

00:14:20.924 --> 00:14:21.924
Can you hear me?

00:14:22.550 --> 00:14:23.550
Excuse me!

00:14:41.310 --> 00:14:42.310
Dad?

00:14:53.741 --> 00:14:54.741
Dad.

00:14:55.864 --> 00:14:56.864
Dad.

00:14:59.851 --> 00:15:01.439
Please open your eyes.

00:15:09.041 --> 00:15:10.208
I'm sorry.

00:15:12.071 --> 00:15:13.692
I'm sorry, Dad.

00:15:14.191 --> 00:15:16.599
I'm sorry I came late, Dad.

00:15:22.926 --> 00:15:24.095
Dad

00:15:24.377 --> 00:15:26.804
had to close his eyes alone in loneliness.

00:15:28.507 --> 00:15:30.816
And the story Mom was going to tell me

00:15:31.616 --> 00:15:34.171
and who the man with her was

00:15:35.401 --> 00:15:37.215
I never got to find out.

00:15:37.666 --> 00:15:39.222
Isn't that the kid from earlier?

00:15:39.821 --> 00:15:42.440
I guess the man
with her wasn't her husband.

00:15:43.091 --> 00:15:44.335
It was an affair, right?

00:15:44.790 --> 00:15:47.679
Having an affair
while her husband was dying...

00:15:47.868 --> 00:15:49.640
I feel so bad for the kid.

00:15:50.265 --> 00:15:52.557
The daughter is paying for
the mother's sins.

00:15:53.021 --> 00:15:54.824
Why would you say something so harsh?

00:15:57.351 --> 00:15:59.709
The truth that couldn't be confirmed

00:16:00.989 --> 00:16:02.734
trapped me in that day.

00:16:04.301 --> 00:16:05.301
What to do!

00:16:05.338 --> 00:16:07.478
Are you okay?

00:16:07.624 --> 00:16:08.826
Are you okay?

00:16:23.461 --> 00:16:24.689
It was from that day

00:16:25.931 --> 00:16:27.832
that I decided to be alone.

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:30.987
Yun Bia!

00:16:33.091 --> 00:16:35.312
Hey, I know you're in there!

00:16:38.421 --> 00:16:39.758
Bia!

00:16:47.491 --> 00:16:48.491
And then

00:16:51.419 --> 00:16:54.060
the one who pulled me out
of the endless darkness was

00:16:56.271 --> 00:16:57.582
It was Jaehee.

00:17:02.650 --> 00:17:03.521
Bia.

00:17:04.176 --> 00:17:05.176
Are you okay?

00:17:10.101 --> 00:17:11.196
What happened?

00:17:12.650 --> 00:17:15.206
That guy grabbed your hand and ran so fast.

00:17:15.492 --> 00:17:17.309
When I got there,
you were already being carried.

00:17:22.041 --> 00:17:23.041
Don't you remember?

00:17:26.651 --> 00:17:27.651
What's going on here?

00:17:29.841 --> 00:17:30.841
Are you okay?

00:17:41.951 --> 00:17:43.054
Well, I'll be going.

00:17:45.911 --> 00:17:48.085
Please have some of this.

00:17:51.930 --> 00:17:52.750
Sure.

00:17:53.681 --> 00:17:54.681
Thank you.

00:18:10.531 --> 00:18:12.797
I'm actually a founding
member of your fan club.

00:18:13.281 --> 00:18:15.911
Before you go, could I get an autograph...

00:18:16.374 --> 00:18:18.022
Or maybe a photo?

00:18:18.616 --> 00:18:20.614
If it's okay with you.

00:18:21.475 --> 00:18:22.781
Maybe your phone number too?

00:18:24.811 --> 00:18:26.572
Of course that's not okay.

00:18:33.400 --> 00:18:34.352
Director!

00:18:36.911 --> 00:18:37.911
Are you okay?

00:18:39.941 --> 00:18:41.132
You're still here?

00:18:43.941 --> 00:18:45.821
Director Yun, this person is...

00:18:45.926 --> 00:18:47.058
A car thief?

00:18:47.760 --> 00:18:48.760
Ah.

00:18:49.045 --> 00:18:50.721
Lovers' quarrel in the elevator?

00:18:53.041 --> 00:18:55.072
He's writer Han Sunho.

00:18:57.401 --> 00:18:58.401
Han Sunho?

00:19:01.070 --> 00:19:02.070
But

00:19:02.321 --> 00:19:03.714
What brings you here?

00:19:05.920 --> 00:19:07.290
I was just passing by.

00:19:08.110 --> 00:19:09.350
You looked like you needed help.

00:19:11.011 --> 00:19:12.416
Thanks for helping out.

00:19:15.881 --> 00:19:17.828
I'm Yun Bia from 'It's You'.

00:19:20.891 --> 00:19:21.891
Let me repay you.

00:19:24.041 --> 00:19:25.041
No need.

00:19:25.431 --> 00:19:26.581
I didn't do it for a reward.

00:19:27.276 --> 00:19:28.906
But it's better to keep things clean.

00:19:29.446 --> 00:19:31.289
To avoid getting tangled up again.

00:19:32.076 --> 00:19:33.076
Well.

00:19:33.999 --> 00:19:35.647
It's money I don't really want.

00:19:37.241 --> 00:19:38.423
What do you mean?

00:19:43.820 --> 00:19:46.404
It's probably cleaner to
just forget it happened.

00:19:49.591 --> 00:19:50.328
I'll be going.

00:19:52.711 --> 00:19:53.711
Hey!

00:19:54.169 --> 00:19:55.426
My autograph...

00:20:02.273 --> 00:20:03.140
Hold on.

00:20:03.351 --> 00:20:04.709
What about the money I invested?

00:20:06.514 --> 00:20:08.344
How is that even possible?

00:20:09.401 --> 00:20:10.915
Tell Park Jungwon?

00:20:11.701 --> 00:20:12.436
Hello?

00:20:12.617 --> 00:20:13.412
Hello!

00:20:23.167 --> 00:20:26.277
Give me my money.

00:20:30.142 --> 00:20:30.682
Goodness.

00:20:30.771 --> 00:20:32.041
How did it go?

00:20:34.210 --> 00:20:35.210
I lost him.

00:20:36.001 --> 00:20:37.001
What do we do?

00:20:37.069 --> 00:20:38.069
What about Manager Han?

00:20:47.951 --> 00:20:49.453
My money!

00:20:56.361 --> 00:20:57.361
Sunho.

00:20:57.851 --> 00:20:59.030
I messed up big time.

00:20:59.051 --> 00:21:01.806
- I'll try to fix it somehow...
- Explain it step by step.

00:21:02.443 --> 00:21:03.535
What happened?

00:21:16.011 --> 00:21:17.095
I told you.

00:21:17.541 --> 00:21:18.541
I borrowed it.

00:21:19.361 --> 00:21:20.361
But seriously.

00:21:21.098 --> 00:21:23.094
Who would lend you that much money?

00:21:26.992 --> 00:21:28.332
Tell me nicely.

00:21:33.961 --> 00:21:35.360
I used our agency.

00:21:36.236 --> 00:21:37.236
As collateral...

00:21:38.843 --> 00:21:39.843
Collateral?

00:21:42.025 --> 00:21:43.174
Are you crazy?

00:21:43.351 --> 00:21:44.068
Sunho!

00:21:44.141 --> 00:21:44.911
Hear me out.

00:21:45.011 --> 00:21:46.268
Come here, Han Baekho, come here.

00:21:46.287 --> 00:21:48.693
- Come here so I can hear you out.
- Listen to me.

00:21:49.251 --> 00:21:51.209
You only call me when you're in trouble?
Aren't you coming here?

00:21:51.228 --> 00:21:52.904
I had a plan, I swear.

00:21:53.771 --> 00:21:54.771
What's that plan?

00:21:54.975 --> 00:21:56.455
I'll have to pull it out of your head.

00:21:56.559 --> 00:21:58.142
- Aren't you coming here?
- I can't!

00:22:06.261 --> 00:22:08.021
- You know it's not our fault, right?
- Hello.

00:22:08.112 --> 00:22:12.202
- Of course, there's no delay.
- Yun is unavailable right now.

00:22:12.511 --> 00:22:13.397
What?

00:22:13.497 --> 00:22:14.598
Withdrawing investment?

00:22:15.130 --> 00:22:17.515
- We'd really appreciate your patience.
- Avoiding you?

00:22:17.930 --> 00:22:20.745
- It won't take long, I promise.
- Director isn't like that!

00:22:21.409 --> 00:22:22.059
Hello.

00:22:22.153 --> 00:22:23.094
[Director Park]

00:22:26.370 --> 00:22:31.718
Due to Park Mo's stock crime scandal,
'It's You', which he modeled for,

00:22:31.819 --> 00:22:34.198
is also expected to
face significant impact.

00:22:34.596 --> 00:22:38.528
Meanwhile, retired writer Han Sunho and
'It's You''s Yun Bia were

00:22:38.628 --> 00:22:43.307
spotted running together,
leading to increased speculation.

00:22:43.876 --> 00:22:47.094
Some speculate they might be
in a relationship,

00:22:47.194 --> 00:22:50.428
drawing more attention to
Director Yun and writer Han Sunho

00:22:50.866 --> 00:22:51.876
Writer Han Sunho's...

00:22:54.320 --> 00:22:55.652
[Han Sunho]

00:23:03.081 --> 00:23:04.222
[Even though I didn't read his
novel, I know of Han Sungho]

00:23:04.255 --> 00:23:05.416
["Our Ending Credit" writer
Han Sungho on and off?]

00:23:10.046 --> 00:23:12.547
Yun Bia and Han Sunho are holding hands.

00:23:13.608 --> 00:23:14.852
Eloping?

00:23:16.420 --> 00:23:17.609
That's ridiculous.

00:23:18.351 --> 00:23:20.486
Sunho in a dating scandal...

00:23:20.855 --> 00:23:23.227
With Director Yun, no less...

00:23:25.462 --> 00:23:28.372
We already have so much to deal with,
this is driving me crazy.

00:23:29.621 --> 00:23:30.621
Director.

00:23:33.051 --> 00:23:34.225
Yun, there's a big problem.

00:23:34.533 --> 00:23:35.233
What?

00:23:35.514 --> 00:23:36.420
A dating rumor?

00:23:37.201 --> 00:23:38.201
No way.

00:23:38.991 --> 00:23:40.061
No way, please.

00:23:40.451 --> 00:23:41.451
More importantly,

00:23:41.604 --> 00:23:44.055
investors are in a frenzy
to withdraw all their funds.

00:23:45.498 --> 00:23:47.589
They're always so impatient.

00:23:48.141 --> 00:23:51.002
Let them regret it if they want to.

00:23:53.361 --> 00:23:54.361
What?

00:23:54.861 --> 00:23:56.113
Do you have a plan?

00:23:57.071 --> 00:23:58.071
Of course.

00:23:59.691 --> 00:24:00.691
Yukyung.

00:24:01.510 --> 00:24:02.286
Yes?

00:24:02.531 --> 00:24:03.827
Please release an article.

00:24:05.361 --> 00:24:06.931
What kind of article?

00:24:13.011 --> 00:24:15.232
'It's You''s Director Yun Bia.

00:24:15.293 --> 00:24:16.414
['It's You''s Director Yun Bia
admits to dating Hang Sungho]

00:24:16.474 --> 00:24:18.149
admits to dating Han Sunho?

00:24:19.161 --> 00:24:20.161
What is this about?

00:24:21.261 --> 00:24:22.533
This woman, seriously...

00:24:24.684 --> 00:24:26.202
What kind of article is this?

00:24:27.075 --> 00:24:28.368
Just get the money first.

00:24:29.156 --> 00:24:29.766
Hey!

00:24:30.043 --> 00:24:30.982
Where are you going?

00:24:32.551 --> 00:24:34.865
Is our company really going under?

00:24:35.142 --> 00:24:36.020
No way!

00:24:36.826 --> 00:24:38.129
Don't worry, Jiyoung.

00:24:38.346 --> 00:24:39.346
You trust me, right?

00:24:41.681 --> 00:24:42.681
Yes.

00:24:43.790 --> 00:24:45.027
Get the money quickly.

00:24:46.231 --> 00:24:47.051
Okay.

00:24:50.101 --> 00:24:53.568
I can't believe I released an article
admitting Sunho's dating...

00:24:55.771 --> 00:24:57.267
What are you thinking?

00:24:57.362 --> 00:24:59.269
You cover an issue with another issue.

00:24:59.792 --> 00:25:00.931
And right now,

00:25:01.488 --> 00:25:02.626
we have an issue.

00:25:03.673 --> 00:25:04.589
An issue?

00:25:05.197 --> 00:25:06.197
Han Sunho,

00:25:06.696 --> 00:25:08.065
he's quite influential.

00:25:08.818 --> 00:25:09.843
Right, Yukyung?

00:25:13.873 --> 00:25:14.786
Yes.

00:25:15.521 --> 00:25:16.521
Of course.

00:25:16.955 --> 00:25:18.703
I looked him up, and Han Sunho

00:25:18.803 --> 00:25:21.232
is doing better than most celebrities.

00:25:21.797 --> 00:25:23.559
He's definitely the top among celebs.

00:25:24.180 --> 00:25:25.670
Will it really help?

00:25:27.030 --> 00:25:28.706
Won't it just cause more noise?

00:25:30.711 --> 00:25:33.611
If we just admit to
the dating rumor, sure.

00:25:34.074 --> 00:25:34.899
Then?

00:25:37.305 --> 00:25:38.305
Kyungtae.

00:25:39.444 --> 00:25:41.038
Did you find Park Jungwon?

00:25:41.397 --> 00:25:42.012
Yes.

00:25:42.441 --> 00:25:44.674
He seems to be hiding in
a motel near Gyeonggi-do.

00:25:44.694 --> 00:25:46.697
I convinced him to meet up with me.

00:25:46.780 --> 00:25:48.219
I calmed him down.

00:25:48.416 --> 00:25:49.416
Good.

00:25:50.066 --> 00:25:51.629
Keep checking on him, please.

00:25:51.951 --> 00:25:52.951
Okay.

00:25:58.717 --> 00:25:59.888
He's out!

00:26:00.331 --> 00:26:01.087
Mr. Han,

00:26:01.107 --> 00:26:04.361
- What's your relationship with Yun Bia?
- Is the dating rumor true?

00:26:04.435 --> 00:26:06.470
There's nothing between us.

00:26:06.605 --> 00:26:07.244
Absolutely not.

00:26:07.282 --> 00:26:09.980
Then why did
Director Yun Bia admit to dating?

00:26:10.113 --> 00:26:12.289
How would I know?
That crazy...

00:26:15.923 --> 00:26:17.882
Go ask her again.

00:26:18.836 --> 00:26:21.238
And please refrain from
baseless speculation.

00:26:23.461 --> 00:26:24.641
Mr. Han, just a moment!

00:26:24.691 --> 00:26:26.971
Then why were you
holding hands and running?

00:26:27.171 --> 00:26:28.301
Just one more word, please!

00:26:30.396 --> 00:26:31.396
No.

00:26:31.706 --> 00:26:33.277
It'll only take a moment.

00:26:33.616 --> 00:26:34.886
I just want to talk, just talk.

00:26:34.906 --> 00:26:38.143
You can't just show up like this.

00:26:38.961 --> 00:26:40.377
Then set up a meeting.

00:26:40.891 --> 00:26:46.455
Director Yun is not holding any meetings
outside of official events right now.

00:26:46.975 --> 00:26:48.724
Then at least connect me by phone.

00:26:48.865 --> 00:26:50.640
I need to hear what she's thinking.

00:26:52.750 --> 00:26:53.677
Excuse me.

00:26:53.921 --> 00:26:54.921
What's going on?

00:26:55.196 --> 00:26:56.935
Could you please escort this person out?

00:26:57.066 --> 00:26:59.502
He's causing a scene by barging in here.

00:26:59.706 --> 00:27:00.706
Causing a scene?

00:27:01.180 --> 00:27:02.006
Please, leave.

00:27:02.148 --> 00:27:03.576
Wait a minute.

00:27:03.756 --> 00:27:04.756
Let's go.

00:27:05.316 --> 00:27:06.316
What's going on?

00:27:06.590 --> 00:27:09.320
I just need to talk to
Director Yun Bia for a moment.

00:27:09.747 --> 00:27:11.367
Let's talk about this!

00:27:11.998 --> 00:27:14.536
- It'll only take a moment!
- You're with the TF team, right?

00:27:16.423 --> 00:27:17.423
Director Yun.

00:27:17.516 --> 00:27:19.882
Writer Han is here causing a scene.

00:27:23.681 --> 00:27:24.681
Where are you going?

00:27:25.023 --> 00:27:26.543
How about a drink for old times' sake?

00:27:27.151 --> 00:27:29.800
I've been so busy,
I haven't spent time with you.

00:27:37.557 --> 00:27:38.837
Let me know if you need anything.

00:27:39.011 --> 00:27:40.011
Thank you.

00:27:43.054 --> 00:27:45.670
They denied the dating rumor,
on their side.

00:27:46.021 --> 00:27:47.118
Doesn't matter.

00:27:47.561 --> 00:27:48.818
In scandals,

00:27:49.061 --> 00:27:51.342
the side that admits has more power.

00:27:54.020 --> 00:27:55.665
How are you planning to handle this?

00:27:56.239 --> 00:27:58.418
We covered up the
Park Jungwon issue for now.

00:27:59.781 --> 00:28:01.305
You're having fun, aren't you?

00:28:05.811 --> 00:28:07.037
By any chance,

00:28:08.270 --> 00:28:09.853
are you really into that guy...

00:28:10.366 --> 00:28:11.555
Are you crazy?

00:28:11.641 --> 00:28:13.381
You know I don't date.

00:28:13.771 --> 00:28:14.348
Right.

00:28:14.677 --> 00:28:15.708
That doesn't make sense.

00:28:16.231 --> 00:28:17.440
And that guy...

00:28:18.040 --> 00:28:19.977
He just broke up recently.

00:28:21.121 --> 00:28:22.351
How do you know that?

00:28:23.141 --> 00:28:25.198
I didn't really want to know either.

00:28:29.071 --> 00:28:30.071
But...

00:28:30.662 --> 00:28:32.676
Didn't Han Sunho see you collapse?

00:28:33.881 --> 00:28:34.455
Yeah.

00:28:34.855 --> 00:28:35.855
That's right.

00:28:36.411 --> 00:28:38.531
Then it's not good to
get more involved, right?

00:28:39.141 --> 00:28:40.745
If he finds out your secret,

00:28:40.805 --> 00:28:41.705
We...

00:28:42.772 --> 00:28:44.515
We just need to take the upper hand.

00:28:46.774 --> 00:28:47.604
How?

00:28:49.520 --> 00:28:50.888
We'll make Han Sunho

00:28:51.933 --> 00:28:54.380
the new prototype model.

00:28:55.190 --> 00:28:56.406
You mean Han Sunho?

00:29:01.934 --> 00:29:04.134
So you couldn't meet her?

00:29:06.011 --> 00:29:08.011
I couldn't even get
in and got kicked out.

00:29:08.641 --> 00:29:10.271
It's like she's avoiding me on purpose.

00:29:15.911 --> 00:29:18.191
Why is there still a fuss
if it's not the person involved?

00:29:18.431 --> 00:29:20.237
Because another person involved
confirmed it.

00:29:21.881 --> 00:29:23.761
What is that woman thinking?

00:29:25.131 --> 00:29:27.104
The Park Jungwon talk is completely gone.

00:29:27.154 --> 00:29:28.810
It's all about you and Yun Bia.

00:29:29.681 --> 00:29:30.681
That woman

00:29:30.946 --> 00:29:33.136
is planning to devour you alive.

00:29:34.651 --> 00:29:35.651
Why on earth?

00:29:36.711 --> 00:29:37.922
Was she a fan of mine?

00:29:38.041 --> 00:29:39.083
Not that.

00:29:39.602 --> 00:29:41.382
She's just diverting attention.

00:29:42.971 --> 00:29:44.846
From a business perspective,

00:29:45.001 --> 00:29:46.331
it's quite a decent strategy.

00:29:46.401 --> 00:29:47.819
Hey, Han Baekho!

00:29:49.815 --> 00:29:51.401
I'm not deaf, you know?

00:29:52.282 --> 00:29:53.163
Give that.

00:29:53.561 --> 00:29:55.256
Stop just drinking.

00:29:56.656 --> 00:29:57.656
What about the money?

00:29:57.696 --> 00:29:58.696
Do you have a plan?

00:29:59.711 --> 00:30:00.530
I do.

00:30:00.721 --> 00:30:01.721
One way.

00:30:01.906 --> 00:30:02.680
What is it?

00:30:03.820 --> 00:30:04.702
Dating.

00:30:05.098 --> 00:30:05.769
What?

00:30:07.414 --> 00:30:08.534
Collaboration, collaboration.

00:30:09.941 --> 00:30:11.229
Let's team up with her.

00:30:11.249 --> 00:30:13.463
I found out she's super rich.

00:30:14.196 --> 00:30:15.196
Are you crazy?

00:30:16.212 --> 00:30:18.266
I'd rather die than
get involved with her again.

00:30:18.347 --> 00:30:19.516
You're already involved.

00:30:19.897 --> 00:30:21.356
Why did you hold her hand then?

00:30:23.521 --> 00:30:25.094
If you were in that situation...

00:30:27.231 --> 00:30:28.869
She almost got into big trouble.

00:30:32.941 --> 00:30:33.730
Then...

00:30:34.044 --> 00:30:35.725
Did she really aim for a dating rumor?

00:30:36.436 --> 00:30:37.436
What?

00:30:38.331 --> 00:30:40.117
She fell for you.

00:30:40.641 --> 00:30:42.727
The prince from a novel,

00:30:43.127 --> 00:30:44.781
who appeared in a dire moment.

00:30:45.556 --> 00:30:47.215
You should write a novel.

00:30:48.551 --> 00:30:51.648
There's already a dating rumor,
just go ahead and date her.

00:30:51.768 --> 00:30:53.811
Looks like you broke up with Serim too.

00:30:54.001 --> 00:30:55.001
Who knows?

00:30:55.041 --> 00:30:56.520
If you become her boyfriend,

00:30:56.720 --> 00:30:57.900
she might pay off our debt.

00:31:01.833 --> 00:31:02.906
[Mina]

00:31:05.881 --> 00:31:07.657
Yeah, Mina.

00:31:09.267 --> 00:31:10.453
What are you doing?

00:31:10.487 --> 00:31:12.021
You should just erase it all.

00:31:12.354 --> 00:31:13.354
Don't!

00:31:14.064 --> 00:31:15.292
Don't.

00:31:21.701 --> 00:31:23.247
Die, 'It's You', die!

00:31:23.333 --> 00:31:24.542
Die, 'It's You', die!

00:31:25.042 --> 00:31:26.670
No, you can't!

00:31:51.301 --> 00:31:52.596
By any chance,

00:31:53.728 --> 00:31:55.619
are you really into that guy.

00:31:58.511 --> 00:31:59.709
Let's just go.

00:32:32.811 --> 00:32:33.811
Mom,

00:32:34.313 --> 00:32:35.313
did you see the article?

00:32:35.596 --> 00:32:36.693
I did.

00:32:37.166 --> 00:32:38.508
Are you finally going to date?

00:32:39.311 --> 00:32:42.491
It's business, not dating.

00:32:43.621 --> 00:32:45.636
But who is that guy?

00:32:45.811 --> 00:32:46.811
Han Sunho?

00:32:47.096 --> 00:32:48.096
He's there.

00:32:48.988 --> 00:32:49.988
My prey.

00:32:51.176 --> 00:32:52.022
Oh my.

00:32:52.331 --> 00:32:54.769
How can you say such
things as a woman?

00:32:54.788 --> 00:32:55.793
It's scary.

00:32:55.879 --> 00:32:56.607
Oh, Mom,

00:32:56.788 --> 00:32:58.710
that's a really outdated comment.

00:33:00.127 --> 00:33:01.127
Anyway,

00:33:02.039 --> 00:33:03.313
he's the one who saved me.

00:33:05.901 --> 00:33:06.901
Saved you?

00:33:08.936 --> 00:33:09.936
You know,

00:33:10.371 --> 00:33:11.789
I didn't collapse today.

00:33:12.604 --> 00:33:13.117
What?

00:33:13.150 --> 00:33:16.713
Dozens were chasing me,
and an hour just passed by.

00:33:17.064 --> 00:33:17.833
So?

00:33:17.996 --> 00:33:20.156
I thought it was over.

00:33:20.606 --> 00:33:21.905
But when I opened my eyes,

00:33:22.227 --> 00:33:24.441
I was running with that guy.

00:33:25.072 --> 00:33:25.754
What?

00:33:26.061 --> 00:33:29.020
I don't remember much after that,

00:33:29.520 --> 00:33:30.520
but anyway,

00:33:31.077 --> 00:33:33.230
it's the first time
I didn't collapse after an hour.

00:33:34.321 --> 00:33:35.079
Maybe...

00:33:35.520 --> 00:33:37.054
you're getting better?

00:33:38.331 --> 00:33:39.189
Is it so?

00:33:39.271 --> 00:33:40.271
Yeah.

00:33:40.446 --> 00:33:42.101
I read in a paper that

00:33:42.311 --> 00:33:45.616
psychogenic breathing difficulties can
suddenly improve.

00:33:45.694 --> 00:33:47.236
It's psychological.

00:33:47.601 --> 00:33:49.860
I emailed it to you.

00:33:49.961 --> 00:33:51.648
Okay, I'll read it.

00:33:52.451 --> 00:33:55.003
Wake me up at 7, I'm going to sleep.

00:33:57.681 --> 00:33:59.449
You didn't collapse.

00:34:05.300 --> 00:34:09.013
Could it be related to that writer,
Han Sunho?

00:34:10.040 --> 00:34:11.566
What do you mean?

00:34:11.586 --> 00:34:13.623
You said it's the first time
you didn't collapse.

00:34:13.826 --> 00:34:16.706
Maybe he's the one
who can cure your symptoms.

00:34:17.957 --> 00:34:19.376
Your destined partner!

00:34:19.456 --> 00:34:20.830
Or something like that.

00:34:24.591 --> 00:34:27.831
If it were that easy,
I'd have been cured long ago.

00:34:27.986 --> 00:34:29.160
I'm going to sleep.

00:34:37.421 --> 00:34:38.622
Traitors...

00:34:38.995 --> 00:34:39.995
Let go!

00:34:40.228 --> 00:34:41.228
I said let go!

00:34:50.271 --> 00:34:51.271
Whoa!

00:34:53.976 --> 00:34:54.878
Hi.

00:34:56.092 --> 00:34:57.092
Director Yun.

00:34:57.406 --> 00:34:59.671
You really managed to escape, huh?

00:35:00.196 --> 00:35:01.565
No, Director Yun.

00:35:02.796 --> 00:35:03.796
Are you serious?

00:35:04.206 --> 00:35:05.369
If you keep this up,

00:35:05.949 --> 00:35:08.315
I might sue you
for confinement and threats.

00:35:08.461 --> 00:35:09.709
Go ahead, try it.

00:35:10.051 --> 00:35:12.122
If you want to pay double the penalty.

00:35:13.991 --> 00:35:16.780
Of course, a peaceful way is better.

00:35:18.921 --> 00:35:19.921
Anyway,

00:35:20.225 --> 00:35:21.245
you're saying

00:35:21.671 --> 00:35:23.427
you'll cut the penalty in half
if I talk?

00:35:23.836 --> 00:35:25.371
That's right.

00:35:25.771 --> 00:35:26.877
Then maybe

00:35:27.763 --> 00:35:30.935
could you waive the damages too?

00:35:33.521 --> 00:35:34.985
San, Kyungtae,

00:35:35.509 --> 00:35:37.046
lock up Park Jungwon again.

00:35:37.946 --> 00:35:39.066
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

00:35:39.556 --> 00:35:41.226
Okay, okay, not there, please!

00:35:41.336 --> 00:35:43.806
I think I got trauma from that place.

00:35:52.471 --> 00:35:53.924
Shall we talk now?

00:35:55.241 --> 00:35:56.610
Why Han Sunho

00:35:57.510 --> 00:35:59.430
came to get you.

00:36:02.101 --> 00:36:03.101
How is it?

00:36:03.331 --> 00:36:04.841
Do you think all our desks will fit?

00:36:05.276 --> 00:36:07.324
I think the desks will fit just fine.

00:36:08.206 --> 00:36:11.435
Hold on, stop shaking,
I can't read this.

00:36:11.526 --> 00:36:13.904
Why are you doing this?

00:36:14.206 --> 00:36:16.940
I think we need to wallpaper this.

00:36:17.016 --> 00:36:18.281
It's painted, so...

00:36:22.780 --> 00:36:23.901
Ouch!

00:36:25.151 --> 00:36:26.151
Ouch.

00:36:26.817 --> 00:36:27.805
Sorry.

00:36:30.582 --> 00:36:31.421
Hey.

00:36:31.691 --> 00:36:32.516
Manager Han.

00:36:32.621 --> 00:36:33.621
Mr. Han.

00:36:37.852 --> 00:36:38.852
Who are you?

00:36:44.491 --> 00:36:45.288
What?

00:36:45.691 --> 00:36:47.037
Did you borrow from loan sharks?

00:36:47.727 --> 00:36:48.645
Not a bank?

00:36:48.686 --> 00:36:49.840
Didn't I tell you?

00:36:50.296 --> 00:36:52.075
They're Park Jungwon's close friends...

00:36:53.054 --> 00:36:54.377
- Are you crazy?
- Hey!

00:36:54.471 --> 00:36:56.761
It's rude to say that
when they're right here.

00:36:57.211 --> 00:36:59.469
We're legitimate businessmen, after all.

00:37:00.190 --> 00:37:01.491
Anyway, about that,

00:37:02.391 --> 00:37:04.234
you lost all the money, right?

00:37:06.638 --> 00:37:07.638
Yesterday.

00:37:08.331 --> 00:37:09.807
Can you pay it back?

00:37:12.331 --> 00:37:15.018
There's still some time
before the due date.

00:37:15.091 --> 00:37:17.868
But giving more time won't
magically make money appear.

00:37:19.041 --> 00:37:19.896
Never mind.

00:37:20.633 --> 00:37:22.150
You're still young,

00:37:22.566 --> 00:37:24.191
losing an organ won't affect your life.

00:37:24.676 --> 00:37:25.896
You'll be fine, right?

00:37:25.957 --> 00:37:26.643
What?

00:37:29.034 --> 00:37:30.944
Come back when the date arrives.

00:37:38.331 --> 00:37:39.331
Hey.

00:37:40.330 --> 00:37:41.124
Hey!

00:37:41.978 --> 00:37:42.900
Yes?

00:37:44.243 --> 00:37:45.342
Aren't you working?

00:37:45.541 --> 00:37:46.203
Yes.

00:37:51.029 --> 00:37:52.135
Just looking at you,

00:37:52.661 --> 00:37:54.858
you remind me a lot of my younger self.

00:37:55.586 --> 00:37:56.787
No way.

00:37:59.631 --> 00:38:00.972
Ah, well, Director,

00:38:01.172 --> 00:38:02.492
I found out that

00:38:05.080 --> 00:38:08.599
this guy's girlfriend handles a lot.

00:38:09.060 --> 00:38:10.060
Handles what?

00:38:10.748 --> 00:38:11.677
Ah, wait, no.

00:38:11.696 --> 00:38:13.116
She handles a lot of money.

00:38:14.479 --> 00:38:15.266
Right?

00:38:15.466 --> 00:38:16.726
Well, that's good news.

00:38:16.976 --> 00:38:18.642
Try asking them to pay it back for you.

00:38:18.856 --> 00:38:21.765
I'm not involved with that woman at all.

00:38:23.481 --> 00:38:25.528
Is it like, "Don't mess with my girl"?

00:38:40.331 --> 00:38:41.691
Shall we talk now?

00:38:42.341 --> 00:38:43.807
Why Han Sunho

00:38:44.011 --> 00:38:46.114
came after Park Jungwon?

00:38:47.451 --> 00:38:48.881
Han Sunho's manager

00:38:49.581 --> 00:38:51.908
borrowed money using
the agency as collateral.

00:38:52.111 --> 00:38:54.503
But they lost all that money?

00:38:55.151 --> 00:38:56.151
That's right.

00:38:56.301 --> 00:38:57.614
Han Sunho found out

00:38:58.314 --> 00:38:59.741
and came after me.

00:39:01.781 --> 00:39:02.781
Decide.

00:39:03.451 --> 00:39:06.455
Either hand over this agency
that's held as collateral

00:39:09.378 --> 00:39:10.821
or pay back the money.

00:39:12.518 --> 00:39:13.902
I'll pay back the money,

00:39:14.265 --> 00:39:15.565
so please leave.

00:39:16.051 --> 00:39:17.214
Alright then.

00:39:17.834 --> 00:39:18.815
Hey, man!

00:39:20.181 --> 00:39:21.591
What are you doing?

00:39:23.927 --> 00:39:24.927
Yes.

00:39:29.041 --> 00:39:30.539
Please follow me.

00:39:31.521 --> 00:39:32.822
Let go of that hand.

00:39:44.057 --> 00:39:45.057
Who?

00:39:45.702 --> 00:39:46.702
Me?

00:39:47.781 --> 00:39:48.987
The woman holding hands

00:39:49.575 --> 00:39:50.707
with that man.

00:39:53.817 --> 00:39:54.817
Ah!

00:39:55.052 --> 00:39:57.321
The girlfriend who's got some money?

00:40:00.551 --> 00:40:01.811
What are you doing?

00:40:01.844 --> 00:40:02.844
Wait!

00:40:04.242 --> 00:40:06.209
If you don't want to get hurt,
put it down.

00:40:21.481 --> 00:40:22.681
You tied it too tightly.

00:40:24.471 --> 00:40:25.471
Hold on a moment.

00:40:25.551 --> 00:40:27.921
My daughter took this
for her kendo lessons, so...

00:40:28.091 --> 00:40:29.091
Why is it...

00:40:29.557 --> 00:40:30.534
Director Sul.

00:40:31.662 --> 00:40:32.662
Hold on.

00:40:48.111 --> 00:40:49.441
What is this supposed to be?

00:40:50.851 --> 00:40:53.456
Why don't you hand over
this collateral to us?

00:40:54.721 --> 00:40:55.721
Hand it over?

00:40:56.311 --> 00:40:57.821
What are you doing right now?

00:40:58.711 --> 00:41:01.504
We mean to take over

00:41:02.044 --> 00:41:04.141
the agency held as collateral.

00:41:05.279 --> 00:41:06.409
What did you say?

00:41:07.941 --> 00:41:08.941
Hold on, hold on.

00:41:10.302 --> 00:41:12.380
I made the deal with them.

00:41:12.772 --> 00:41:14.918
If you want this collateral,

00:41:15.713 --> 00:41:17.506
this money won't even come close.

00:41:17.606 --> 00:41:20.082
Even with the principal
and interest, this...

00:41:20.182 --> 00:41:22.031
- Seems like there's a lot left...
- Can you be quiet?

00:41:23.031 --> 00:41:25.602
People breaking the law are
always so bold.

00:41:25.781 --> 00:41:26.469
What?

00:41:29.011 --> 00:41:32.120
Illegal contract, exceeding legal rates,
illegal collection.

00:41:33.528 --> 00:41:35.311
Shall we take this to court?

00:41:35.981 --> 00:41:38.308
If you want the contract declared void,

00:41:45.621 --> 00:41:47.531
if not, let's pretend
this deal never happened.

00:41:49.201 --> 00:41:50.466
Hold on, hold on.

00:41:51.420 --> 00:41:53.483
You ladies have quite the temper.

00:41:54.170 --> 00:41:56.284
It's just a figure of speech, you know.

00:41:56.894 --> 00:41:58.668
How about we sign right away?

00:41:59.190 --> 00:42:00.483
Shall we stamp it?

00:42:34.011 --> 00:42:35.426
Sorry, but

00:42:36.520 --> 00:42:38.914
could you wait a moment before using it?

00:42:39.355 --> 00:42:40.116
What?

00:42:41.245 --> 00:42:42.245
I'm sorry.

00:42:44.271 --> 00:42:45.671
What? Did you rent the whole place?

00:42:47.521 --> 00:42:49.212
We'll just use the bathroom downstairs.

00:42:50.276 --> 00:42:51.355
Unbelievable.

00:43:05.802 --> 00:43:07.490
[Safe]

00:43:18.881 --> 00:43:20.997
We seem to meet quite often, don't we?

00:43:22.911 --> 00:43:25.595
Didn't you say it's better to keep things
clean to avoid getting entangled?

00:43:25.851 --> 00:43:27.297
I came to repay the favor.

00:43:27.621 --> 00:43:30.280
It's just that the scale got a bit bigger.

00:43:30.856 --> 00:43:32.302
Was collapsing in front of me

00:43:32.741 --> 00:43:33.857
part of the plan too?

00:43:35.146 --> 00:43:37.086
You're overthinking it.

00:43:37.356 --> 00:43:38.765
I'm not a fortune teller.

00:43:38.865 --> 00:43:40.557
Could I have predicted that too?

00:43:40.641 --> 00:43:42.105
Then what's with the public romance?

00:43:43.350 --> 00:43:44.919
How did you know about our situation?

00:43:45.016 --> 00:43:46.890
I did some research.

00:43:47.226 --> 00:43:49.639
Information is key in business.

00:43:49.836 --> 00:43:50.836
Isn't that snooping?

00:43:50.863 --> 00:43:53.242
Didn't you start it
by holding my hand first?

00:43:53.333 --> 00:43:55.043
You held my hand, remember?

00:43:56.171 --> 00:43:57.171
I did.

00:43:57.961 --> 00:43:59.189
That was my goodwill.

00:44:00.035 --> 00:44:01.751
But you used it maliciously.

00:44:02.111 --> 00:44:03.539
Not maliciously,

00:44:04.553 --> 00:44:05.553
but as a return favor.

00:44:06.441 --> 00:44:09.491
- This time, I'm the one offering a hand.
- You took it by force and then-

00:44:09.591 --> 00:44:11.751
Isn't it better than
letting it fall to loan sharks?

00:44:16.001 --> 00:44:17.934
Instead, I'll make you an offer.

00:44:19.810 --> 00:44:21.202
It's a collaboration contract.

00:44:21.331 --> 00:44:24.440
Sign it, and once the second generation
of 'ForMe' is successfully developed,

00:44:24.816 --> 00:44:26.663
I'll return the agency to you.

00:44:26.718 --> 00:44:27.718
Really?

00:44:27.767 --> 00:44:29.751
And the money we owe?

00:44:29.846 --> 00:44:31.641
Sign it, and consider it paid.

00:44:32.136 --> 00:44:33.508
If you don't like that,

00:44:34.888 --> 00:44:36.152
you can just pay it back.

00:44:36.659 --> 00:44:38.540
Of course, I'll sign it.

00:44:46.331 --> 00:44:48.183
What exactly do you want from us?

00:44:50.551 --> 00:44:52.127
To be precise,

00:44:52.614 --> 00:44:54.034
not us,

00:44:55.229 --> 00:44:56.229
but you.

00:44:56.357 --> 00:44:57.180
What is it?

00:44:57.927 --> 00:44:59.120
What do you want from me?

00:45:00.011 --> 00:45:01.220
Sell it to me.

00:45:03.433 --> 00:45:04.320
What?

00:45:05.621 --> 00:45:06.911
I'll buy it.

00:45:06.991 --> 00:45:08.123
You.